@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.16) / wp.abs(v1 + 0.73)))
    v0 = (tmp + ((tmp + 0.31 / tmp + 0.55) / wp.abs(v0 + 0.34)))
    v2 = (0.41 - tmp)
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.35)) + v1)
    v0 = tmp
    v2 = (0.36 + ((v0 + 0.23 / v1 + 0.45) / (v2 + 0.24 - v0 + 0.72)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
